Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.55,0:01:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家快来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.65,0:01:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鼬鼠丫头\N在山上精神特别好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.89,0:02:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小操 翁爷爷在京都\N恐怕非常担心你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.26,0:02:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在大阪有写信给他\N没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.36,0:02:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 绯村你们的旅行\N为什么这么不顺利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.17,0:02:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 在清水因为船故障\N而被赶上岸之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都用步行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿得不能动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往这边走就到箱根了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,箱根是很出名的温泉乡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过而不入太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.52,0:02:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是 去吃一顿饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.69,0:02:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后泡温泉\N消除旅行的疲倦也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就住在箱根吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.06,0:02:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.40,0:02:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七十八话\N美术学生思念的女性\N箱根温泉街的念爱骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.10,0:02:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好饱好饱 啊 好饱好饱\N再也吃不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.21,0:02:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房间与料理都最高级的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.41,0:02:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这里离东京就很近了\N偶尔就是应该享受一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.12,0:03:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 恕我失礼问个问题\N请问你们付帐没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这房间是最高级的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 还有剩很多路费吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.96,0:03:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩 剑心\N交给你保管的钱没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我保管在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.94,0:03:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.84,0:03:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会剑心 你把钱搞丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.81,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…就是那个该不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还敢笑 快找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.63,0:03:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.43,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 客人们身无分文了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大掌柜 糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 你那边也有争执啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.04,0:03:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然来了一整团客人\N我们忙着招待不过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.54,0:04:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在人手不足 伤脑筋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.45,0:04:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大掌柜 让我工作付住宿费吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.82,0:04:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们剑心组是团结一心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粗活包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.16,0:04:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N我可是京都出名的料理亭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葵屋的卷町操呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种工作我太熟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对 不是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底还缺少什么\N缺少什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.65,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭已经准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃过饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰 可能我们搞错房间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.53,0:04:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.46,0:04:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.13,0:04:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 等等呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是她！就是她！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心呀 这就是天无绝人之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差点以为完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像还可以赚到东京的旅行费
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.32,0:05:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的疏忽…\N大家对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是剑心组哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了终极的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.49,0:05:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不输给那星星的永远的光辉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所寻求的答案！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.08,0:05:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流汗之后洗澡真享受\N太舒服了 太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.85,0:05:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小操\N我家的剑心连累大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 无所谓啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.19,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你喊剑心是你家的\N真的好亲密哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 我没那意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.73,0:06:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了 小操\N我跟剑心还不是什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.87,0:06:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就猜到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.14,0:06:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那方面态度完全暧昧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知他心里是怎么看你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.48,0:06:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看他\N又不像是对女人没兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是另有喜欢的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是忘不了过去的女人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.88,0:06:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是年纪差太多\N没有把阿薰当成女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.02,0:06:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小操 你不用担心我了\N反倒是你自己呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.56,0:06:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无所谓的\N不管苍紫大人怎样想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意一辈子不变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.58,0:06:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.62,0:06:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.79,0:06:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色、色、色狼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰 小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.26,0:07:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.67,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准看！别过来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.17,0:07:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 这是第四次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.68,0:07:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被绯村看见了 怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.52,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的好奇心太强了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.79,0:07:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种人应该处死！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我绝不是坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.93,0:07:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.53,0:07:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在东京学习西洋画的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫做东山龙三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是学画的学生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.17,0:07:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这几年我不断为艺术是什么\N这基本的问题而苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.01,0:07:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 为了找出那答案\N我下定决心出来旅行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.22,0:08:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我还是找不出答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.22,0:08:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是过着空虚的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.39,0:08:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后我终于彻底丧失信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.06,0:08:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一眼看到她时\N我才恍然大悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言 艺术是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.74,0:08:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就世上最美的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.84,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是要描绘出终极之美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终极之美是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.51,0:08:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太困难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简单讲\N就是你找到超级大美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 明知她在入浴中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.19,0:08:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是忍不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.42,0:08:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太想把她的身影\N画进这本素描簿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入浴中 不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.80,0:08:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解我的美丽的人\N世上只要有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫大人就足够了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是小姐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 是阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.45,0:09:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了艺术 我必需画你才行\N请你当我的模特儿吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.06,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道艺术是什么\N但是你把我画成画是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在乐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她乐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.58,0:09:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛\N我是跟阿薰在一起的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.65,0:09:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一间要准备\N请你们快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.69,0:09:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被当奴隶差遣\N阿薰这时候却偷懒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰并不是在玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.50,0:09:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说\N她是为了艺术 艺术呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.34,0:10:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上最美丽的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是头一次被男人这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.25,0:10:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心从不夸奖我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.09,0:10:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知他是没有看人的眼光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是神经太迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这种感觉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.30,0:10:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 请快去菊之间吧\N那里有团体客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.87,0:10:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 画得跟阿薰一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.98,0:10:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小操\N他说这个只是草图而已呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.65,0:10:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实有两把刷子\N能把阿薰画成大美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.85,0:10:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴 弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.76,0:10:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你挺有实力的嘛\N对你刮目相看了 小伙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.79,0:10:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.73,0:10:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是个空壳子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是真正的阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对呀 难得画那么漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.21,0:11:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看来确实是阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.68,0:11:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这张画\N没有画入最重要的心呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我看不见阿薰的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.86,0:11:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.03,0:11:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我爱上了阿薰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.68,0:11:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱上…小姐了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.76,0:12:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 画着她的时候\N我忍不住想更了解她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.96,0:12:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 那时候我已经掉入爱河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是讽刺的是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.00,0:12:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这激热的思念蒙蔽了我的双眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰的心啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.91,0:12:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见阿薰的心之后\N恐怕连魔鬼都会逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰 请跟我交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.62,0:12:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我相信总有一天\N我一定能看清楚你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.86,0:12:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的艺术完成之日！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说 我也很为难…\N好伤脑筋呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.03,0:12:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对呀 阿薰已经有绯村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.70,0:12:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 小操真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰 菊之间在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.48,0:13:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？阿薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.02,0:13:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.86,0:13:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见 虽然不很顺利\N但是小姐的心意很明显了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.94,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我泼你冷水\N你还是死心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.44,0:13:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样\N我好不容易找到的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.22,0:13:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.48,0:13:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呀！小伙子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我放弃阿薰 我不如去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.76,0:13:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你要死是你的自由\N别选我们在的时候！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.60,0:13:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉\N不可以轻易把自杀挂在嘴上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.30,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 我是认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.44,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你是男子汉 拜托你\N帮我想想办法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.98,0:14:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被人这样要求\N身为男子汉是无法拒绝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你干脆帮帮他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.92,0:14:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别给我多嘴\N我最讨厌惹上麻烦事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.46,0:14:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别叫别叫 我有个好主意\N耳朵凑过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.63,0:14:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子 看在你够热诚\N我可以帮你的忙没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是有个条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,条件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天日落之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.74,0:14:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能够打中剑心一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.88,0:14:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时我就负责撮合你与小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我从没学过剑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么此事当我没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.79,0:14:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 这是男人跟男人的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.23,0:14:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你还办不到\N就要勇敢忘记我们小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧 小伙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.87,0:15:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 左之助\N我也是男人 绝不食言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.34,0:15:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到阿薰的心\N完成我的艺术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场决斗我一定要赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.18,0:15:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记说一句话了\N别看剑心呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.25,0:15:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可是幕末时候\N在京都连新撰组都会害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.12,0:15:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被称为斩人拔刀斋的男人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就小心行事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟对手是斩人拔刀斋嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.27,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好笑了\N听到是斩人拔刀斋就怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.11,0:15:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样那家伙应该醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.44,0:15:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们别把我的竹刀\N拿去做那种用途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正他会很快就死心\N拿来还了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.98,0:15:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子…不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的去偷袭绯村了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.60,0:16:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得早点做完去准备晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.07,0:16:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加快一下节奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对手是幕末时候的杀人狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.94,0:16:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正面攻他是绝对没胜算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要在背后出其不意偷袭\N赌上我的一线希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.35,0:16:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.39,0:16:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好像听到人的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真的去偷袭剑心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知是不自量力\N还是不要命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的竹刀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…百合之间确实是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿剑 这边啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿剑 快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.07,0:17:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等着瞧吧 阿薰 我一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.51,0:17:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天总感到身边有奇怪的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是我累了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟工作了一整天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.93,0:17:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 无法用手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那位学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.35,0:17:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这样自作主张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我没告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.12,0:18:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你放心吧\N以他的身手呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算花上一百年时间\N也不可能打倒绯村的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.29,0:18:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快超过限定时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.16,0:18:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我担心的是龙三郎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必需要阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他受重伤就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.94,0:18:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他应该死心了\N不过为了以防万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是去找他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.97,0:18:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 找绯村最快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.44,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心应该上山\N采集晚餐要用的山菜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.28,0:18:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一起去 我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.86,0:18:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.66,0:18:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我采到这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.87,0:18:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来什么事也没发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说得没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都聚在这里是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还没放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.81,0:18:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的竹刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助这到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的 剑心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.76,0:19:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.16,0:19:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰别过去 那是雀蜂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 你救那个学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.49,0:19:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好只是手臂受伤\N你别太让人担心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.53,0:19:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.01,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别太沮丧啦 小伙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.94,0:20:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来…原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.71,0:20:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰的心中\N充满了对绯村的情意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.55,0:20:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那美丽是爱着绯村的心\N的一种表现啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.59,0:20:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能画 现在我能画出来\N画下阿薰的真实模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.23,0:20:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.44,0:20:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才能清楚发现\N活下去的艺术之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.21,0:20:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 龙三郎还有\N艺术这条很棒的道路呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.91,0:20:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.95,0:20:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也祝阿薰你幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.98,0:20:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这是送给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.82,0:20:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 阿薰\N各位也保重 再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比阿薰漂亮的美女很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦 你话太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.50,0:21:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们再工作两三天\N就可以回东京了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面就是东海官道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.51,0:21:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直走就到东京了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.18,0:21:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操你果然是想念京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.29,0:21:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 我一直很在意\N那张画画了什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.29,0:21:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 我想回到东京以后\N再打开来看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别小气了 让我看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.96,0:21:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.67,0:21:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.94,0:21:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能看一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.44,0:21:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说主题是女神的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.21,0:21:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像不像我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.55,0:21:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.52,0:21:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不看了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 弥彦 我们先赶路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.59,0:22:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然这么慌张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.77,0:22:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什、什么 这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.34,0:22:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了 还说是女神的微笑
